<HEADLINE>
FT  11 JUN 94 / UK Company News: PSB and ICD call off talks
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Talks between PSB, the direct marketing group, and International
Communications &amp; Data have been terminated.
The shares of ICD closed 1 1/2 p lower at 9 1/2 p.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
